v0.1, 20-Feb-2012 -- Initial release.

v0.2, 21-Sep-2012
o Add log rotation functionality.  This prevents having to rotate the daemon
  and consequently, re-enter the passphrase.
o Use getpass module instead of raw_input for passphrase prompt.
o Don't prepend https url requests with http://.
o Add an expire command to delete Nyms with expired keys.
o Correct a dictionary naming error on Duplicate message.
o Add a configuration option to specify which mail header to check for
  recipients.

v0.3, Not yet released
o Trap new nym requests that have no email addresses on the key.
o Check for malformed Content-Type returned during geturl().
o Convert uppercase chars in the recipient address before validation.
o Trap unexpected responses from Webservers during URL retrieval.
